\size larger
\begin_inset Formula $\exists x_{2}\in[a,b]:f(x_{2})$
\end_inset

 — 
\begin_inset Formula $\min f(x)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\size larger
Так как функция — не константа, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x_{2})<f(x_{1})$
